                        "id": "18074709314023522",
                        "text": "Here\u2019s part 2 of the best eats that I had on my trip to JAPAN!\n\n5. Cremia soft serve (multiple locations)\n4. Tuna stand at Tsukiji Market (Tokyo)\n3. Imo Pippi (Tokyo)\n2. Tonkatsu Marushichi (Tokyo)\n1. Men-Ya Inoichi (Kyoto)\n\nHonorable Mention\n- Iyoshi Cola (Tokyo)\n- Giraffa (Tokyo)\n- Hatoya Matcha (Multiple locations)\n- 7-Eleven (everywhere)\n- Musk melon (got it at my hotel buffets)\n\nAnd check out my Japan playlist to see my video with number 6-10 favorite eats!\n\n#japaneats #japantravelguide\n#wheretoeatjapan"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
